snippet.title: Worse Than Death - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
A scary. emotional thriller about a high school reunion that goes horribly wrong!  Worse Than Death is the chilling follow-up to indie horror hit Home, and it's coming soon to PlayStation 4, Nintendo Switch, Steam and the App Store!

Read an EXCLUSIVE prequel story at https://discord.gg/RwaUFkW

+ OFFICIAL Website: http://www.worsethandeathgame.com
+ Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/benjaminrivers
+ Discord: https://discord.gg/RwaUFkW
